#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "broken pursuer"
msgid_plural "broken pursuers"
msgstr[0] "損壞的追擊者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broken pursuer'}
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid ""
"A broken pursuer drone, now wrecked and motionless.  It could be gutted for "
"spare parts."
msgstr "一架損壞的追擊者無人機，現已殘破且靜止不動。可拆解以獲取備用零件。"

#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "broken seeker"
msgid_plural "broken seekers"
msgstr[0] "損壞的搜尋者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broken seeker'}
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid ""
"A broken seeker drone, now crumpled and fallen. It could be gutted for "
"parts."
msgstr "一架損壞的追蹤無人機，現已扭曲墜毀。可拆解獲取零件。"

#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "inactive seeker"
msgid_plural "inactive seekers"
msgstr[0] "休眠追蹤者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'inactive seeker'}
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid ""
"An autonomous drone designed to seek and exterminate enemy combatants. It's "
"capable of delivering a single burst of 9mm rounds before closing to finish "
"off its prey. It's currently inactive but ready to be deployed."
msgstr "專為搜尋殲滅敵方戰鬥人員設計的自主無人機。能在接近目標前發射一輪9毫米子彈，隨後近身終結獵物。當前處於休眠狀態，隨時可部署。"

#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "broken hunter drone"
msgid_plural "broken hunter drones"
msgstr[0] "損壞的獵殺無人機"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broken hunter drone'}
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid ""
"A broken hunter drone, now burnt and unpowered.  It could be gutted for "
"parts."
msgstr "一架損壞的獵殺無人機，現已燒燬斷電。可拆解獲取零件。"

#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "inactive hunter drone"
msgid_plural "inactive hunter drones"
msgstr[0] "休眠獵殺無人機"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'inactive hunter drone'}
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid ""
"A dog-sized military drone designed to hunt out and exterminate enemy "
"combatants. With a pair of barbed mandibles, it can prevent its prey from "
"escaping. It is currently inactive and ready to be deployed."
msgstr "犬型軍用無人機，專為追獵殲滅敵方戰鬥人員設計。配備一對帶刺顎鉗，能阻止獵物逃脫。當前處於休眠狀態，隨時可部署。"

#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "broken chaser drone"
msgid_plural "broken chaser drones"
msgstr[0] "損壞的追擊無人機"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broken chaser drone'}
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid ""
"A broken chaser drone, now shattered and disarmed. It could be gutted for "
"parts."
msgstr "一架損壞的追擊無人機，現已支離破碎、武器失效。可拆解獲取零件。"

#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "inactive chaser"
msgid_plural "inactive chasers"
msgstr[0] "休眠追擊者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'inactive chaser'}
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid ""
"A relentless hoverdrone designed to chase down and exterminate enemy robots."
" It's capable of firing three .50bmg rounds before closing in to finish off "
"its prey. It is currently inactive and ready to be deployed."
msgstr "為追獵殲滅敵方機器人設計的 relentless 懸浮無人機。能發射三發.50bmg子彈後近身終結獵物。當前處於休眠狀態，隨時可部署。"

#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "broken manhack"
msgid_plural "broken manhacks"
msgstr[0] "損壞的獵殺機"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broken manhack'}
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid ""
"A broken manhack. It's far too damaged to be repaired, but could still be "
"gutted for spare parts."
msgstr "一架損壞的獵殺機。損毀嚴重無法修復，但仍可拆解獲取備用零件。"

#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "inactive venomhack"
msgid_plural "inactive venomhacks"
msgstr[0] "休眠毒刺機"

#. ~ Use action friendly_msg for {'str': 'inactive venomhack'}.
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid ""
"The venomhack flies from your hand and begins dripping toxic chemicals."
msgstr "毒刺機從你手中飛出，開始滴落有毒化學物質。"

#. ~ Use action hostile_msg for {'str': 'inactive venomhack'}.
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "You misprogram the venomhack; it's hostile!"
msgstr "你錯誤編程了毒刺機；它變得敵對！"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'inactive venomhack'}
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid ""
"A manhack converted into a venomous stinging drone. The stingers of giant "
"insects have been added in place of blades. It is currently inactive and "
"ready to be deployed."
msgstr "改裝為帶毒刺攻擊無人機的獵殺機。刀片被替換為巨型昆蟲的毒刺。當前處於休眠狀態，隨時可部署。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broken manhack'}
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid ""
"A broken venom hack. It's far too damaged to be repaired, but could be "
"gutted for parts."
msgstr "一架損壞的毒刺機。損毀嚴重無法修復，但可拆解獲取零件。"

#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "inactive distractron"
msgid_plural "inactive distractrons"
msgstr[0] "休眠干擾機"

#. ~ Use action friendly_msg for {'str': 'inactive distractron'}.
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "The distractron flies from your hand and lights up."
msgstr "干擾機從你手中飛出並亮起燈光。"

#. ~ Use action hostile_msg for {'str': 'inactive distractron'}.
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "You misprogram the distractron; it's hostile."
msgstr "你錯誤編程了干擾機；它變得敵對。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'inactive distractron'}
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid ""
"A manhack hastily rewired into a distraction device. The main blades have "
"been removed, making it harmless, but also more difficult to hit. Mp3's of "
"pre-Cataclysmic folk music have been added as a further distraction. It is "
"currently inactive and ready to be deployed."
msgstr ""
"匆忙改裝為干擾裝置的獵殺機。主刀片已移除使其無害，但也更難被擊中。額外添加了災變前民間音樂的Mp3文件以增強幹擾效果。當前處於休眠狀態，隨時可部署。"

#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "broken distractron"
msgid_plural "broken distractrons"
msgstr[0] "損壞的干擾機"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broken distractron'}
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid ""
"A broken distractron. It's too damaged to fix, but could be gutted for "
"parts."
msgstr "一架損壞的干擾機。損毀過度無法修復，但可拆解獲取零件。"

#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "inactive smokehack"
msgid_plural "inactive smokehacks"
msgstr[0] "休眠煙霧機"

#. ~ Use action friendly_msg for {'str': 'inactive smokehack'}.
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "The smokehack flies from your hand and ignites."
msgstr "煙霧機從你手中飛出並點燃。"

#. ~ Use action hostile_msg for {'str': 'inactive smokehack'}.
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "You misprogram the smokehack; it's hostile."
msgstr "你錯誤編程了煙霧機；它變得敵對。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'inactive smokehack'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'smokehack'}
#: .\jrr_items.json .\jrr_rigged_bots.json
msgid ""
"A manhack tinkered into a flying smoke generator. It makes a less effective "
"weapon, but provides a good smoke screen. It's currently inactive and ready "
"to be deployed."
msgstr "改裝為飛行煙霧發生器的獵殺機。作為武器效果較差，但能提供良好的煙霧掩護。當前處於休眠狀態，隨時可部署。"

#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "broken eyebot"
msgid_plural "broken eyebots"
msgstr[0] "損壞的眼球機器人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broken eyebot'}
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid ""
"A broken eyebot, now fallen and sightless. It could be gutted for parts or "
"jury-rigged into a new type of bot."
msgstr "一架損壞的眼球機器人，現已墜落失明。可拆解獲取零件，或臨時改裝成新型機器人。"

#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "broken orb bot"
msgid_plural "broken orb bots"
msgstr[0] "損壞的球形機器人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broken orb bot'}
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid ""
"A broken orb bot, now dark and lifeless. It could be repaired or stripped "
"down to its eyebot frame."
msgstr "一個損壞的球形機器人，如今黯淡無光、毫無生氣。它可以被修復，或者拆解成眼球機器人框架。"

#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "inactive orb bot"
msgid_plural "inactive orb bots"
msgstr[0] "未激活的球形機器人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'inactive orb bot'}
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid ""
"A salvaged eyebot patched up with low-grade electronics. The camera has been"
" replaced with a powerful floodlight. It's currently inactive but ready to "
"be deployed."
msgstr "一個用低端電子元件修補過的回收眼球機器人。攝像頭已被替換為強力泛光燈。它目前處於未激活狀態，但已準備好部署。"

#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "broken skitterbot"
msgid_plural "broken skitterbots"
msgstr[0] "損壞的爬行機器人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broken skitterbot'}
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid ""
"A broken skitterbot, now sad and motionless.  It could be gutted for parts "
"or jury-rigged into a new type of bot."
msgstr "一個損壞的爬行機器人，如今悲傷地靜止不動。它可以被拆解獲取零件，或者臨時改裝成新型機器人。"

#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "broken skaterbot"
msgid_plural "broken skaterbots"
msgstr[0] "損壞的滑行機器人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broken skaterbot'}
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid ""
"A broken skaterbot, now drained and unmoving. Could be repaired or stripped "
"down to its skitter bot frame."
msgstr "一個損壞的滑行機器人，如今能量耗盡、一動不動。它可以被修復，或者拆解成爬行機器人框架。"

#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "inactive skaterbot"
msgid_plural "inactive skaterbots"
msgstr[0] "未激活的滑行機器人"

#. ~ Use action friendly_msg for {'str': 'inactive skaterbot'}.
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "The skaterbot spins its wheels and emits a cascade of sparks."
msgstr "滑行機器人轉動輪子，迸發出一連串火花。"

#. ~ Use action hostile_msg for {'str': 'inactive skaterbot'}.
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "You misprogram the skaterbot; it's hostile."
msgstr "你錯誤編程了滑行機器人；它變得敵對。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'inactive skaterbot'}
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid ""
"A salvaged skitterbot rewired with consumer grade electronics. Small wheels "
"have been kludged to the ends of its insectoid legs. It's inactive but ready"
" to be deployed."
msgstr "一個用消費級電子元件重新接線的回收爬行機器人。其昆蟲狀腿部末端被粗糙地加裝了小輪子。它處於未激活狀態，但已準備好部署。"

#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "broken police bot"
msgid_plural "broken police bots"
msgstr[0] "損壞的警用機器人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broken police bot'}
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid ""
"A broken police bot, now crushed and dirty. It could be gutted for parts or "
"jury-rigged into a new type of bot."
msgstr "一個損壞的警用機器人，如今被壓扁且骯髒不堪。它可以被拆解獲取零件，或者臨時改裝成新型機器人。"

#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "broken shockbot"
msgid_plural "broken shockbots"
msgstr[0] "損壞的電擊機器人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broken shockbot'}
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid ""
"A broken shockbot, now powerless and inert. It could be repaired or stripped"
" down to it's police bot frame."
msgstr "一個損壞的電擊機器人，如今失去動力、毫無反應。它可以被修復，或者拆解成警用機器人框架。"

#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "inactive shockbot"
msgid_plural "inactive shockbots"
msgstr[0] "未激活的電擊機器人"

#. ~ Use action friendly_msg for {'str': 'inactive shockbot'}.
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "The shockbot emits a low electric hum and begins to amble about."
msgstr "電擊機器人發出低沉的電流嗡鳴聲，開始緩慢移動。"

#. ~ Use action hostile_msg for {'str': 'inactive shockbot'}.
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "You misprogram the shockbot!"
msgstr "你錯誤編程了電擊機器人！"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'inactive shockbot'}
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid ""
"A salvaged police bot mended with old circuitboards and car batteries. It's "
"been covered with electrified barbed wire and given a makeshift shock gun. "
"It is currently inactive and ready to be deployed."
msgstr "一個用舊電路板和汽車電池修補過的回收警用機器人。它被覆蓋了帶電鐵絲網，並配備了一把臨時電擊槍。目前處於未激活狀態，已準備好部署。"

#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "broken riot control bot"
msgid_plural "broken riot control bots"
msgstr[0] "損壞的防暴控制機器人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broken riot control bot'}
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid ""
"A broken riot control bot, now deformed and gasless. It could be gutted for "
"parts or jury-rigged into a new type of bot."
msgstr "一個損壞的防暴控制機器人，如今變形且氣體耗盡。它可以被拆解獲取零件，或者臨時改裝成新型機器人。"

#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "broken solar bot"
msgid_plural "broken solar bots"
msgstr[0] "損壞的太陽能機器人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broken solar bot'}
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid ""
"A broken solar bot, now dark and shattered. It could be repaired or stripped"
" down to its original frame."
msgstr "一個損壞的太陽能機器人，如今黯淡無光、支離破碎。它可以被修復，或者拆解回原始框架。"

#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "inactive chicken walker"
msgid_plural "inactive chicken walkers"
msgstr[0] "未激活的雞形步行機"

#. ~ Use action friendly_msg for {'str': 'inactive chicken walker'}.
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "The chicken bot rolls out and begins acquiring targets."
msgstr "雞形機器人出動並開始鎖定目標。"

#. ~ Use action hostile_msg for {'str': 'inactive chicken walker'}.
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid ""
"The chicken bot swivels its turret and aims directly at you.  Don your brown"
" pants!"
msgstr "雞形機器人旋轉炮塔並直接瞄準你。快穿上你的棕色褲子！"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'inactive chicken walker'}
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid ""
"This is an inactive chicken walker.  Using this item involves placing it on "
"the ground, loading the unit with the factory-loaded 5.56 rounds and 40mm "
"cartridge grenades in your inventory (if you wish to divide your ammunition,"
" set aside whatever ammunition you do NOT want to give the robot) and "
"turning it on.  If reprogrammed and rewired successfully the tank drone will"
" then identify you as a friendly, roam around or follow you, and attack all "
"enemies with a built-in firearm and grenade launcher."
msgstr ""
"這是一臺未激活的雞形步行機。使用此物品需將其放置在地面，從庫存中為它裝載出廠預裝的5.56毫米子彈和40毫米榴彈（若想分配彈藥，請先預留你不想給機器人的部分），然後啟動。若成功重編程並重新接線，坦克無人機會將你識別為友方，四處巡邏或跟隨你，並用內置槍械與榴彈發射器攻擊所有敵人。"

#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "inactive tank drone"
msgid_plural "inactive tank drones"
msgstr[0] "未激活的坦克無人機"

#. ~ Use action friendly_msg for {'str': 'inactive tank drone'}.
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "The tank drone rolls out and begins acquiring targets."
msgstr "坦克無人機出動並開始鎖定目標。"

#. ~ Use action hostile_msg for {'str': 'inactive tank drone'}.
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid ""
"The tank drone swivels its turret and aims directly at you.  Don your brown "
"pants!"
msgstr "坦克無人機旋轉炮塔並直接瞄準你。快穿上你的棕色褲子！"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'inactive tank drone'}
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid ""
"This is an inactive Beagle Mini-Tank UGV.  Using this item involves placing "
"it on the ground, loading the unit with the factory-loaded 5.56 rounds and "
"40mm cartridge grenades in your inventory (if you wish to divide your "
"ammunition, set aside whatever ammunition you do NOT want to give the robot)"
" and turning it on.  If reprogrammed and rewired successfully the tank drone"
" will then identify you as a friendly, roam around or follow you, and attack"
" all enemies with a built-in firearm and grenade launcher."
msgstr ""
"這是一臺未激活的Beagle迷你坦克UGV。使用此物品需將其放置在地面，從庫存中為它裝載出廠預裝的5.56毫米子彈和40毫米榴彈（若想分配彈藥，請先預留你不想給機器人的部分），然後啟動。若成功重編程並重新接線，坦克無人機會將你識別為友方，四處巡邏或跟隨你，並用內置槍械與榴彈發射器攻擊所有敵人。"

#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "Pathfinder chassis"
msgid_plural "Pathfinder chassis"
msgstr[0] "探路者底盤"

#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': 'Pathfinder chassis'}
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid ""
"What's left when you remove all moving parts and electronics.  It's the "
"skeleton and armor of the pathfinder."
msgstr "移除所有活動部件和電子設備後的剩餘部分。這是探路者的骨架與裝甲。"

#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "Regulator chassis"
msgid_plural "Regulator chassis"
msgstr[0] "調節者底盤"

#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': 'Regulator chassis'}
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid ""
"What's left when you remove all moving parts and electronics.  It's the "
"skeleton and armor of the Regulator tank."
msgstr "移除所有活動部件和電子設備後的剩餘部分。這是調節者坦克的骨架與裝甲。"

#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "inactive solar bot"
msgid_plural "inactive solar bots"
msgstr[0] "未激活的太陽能機器人"

#. ~ Use action friendly_msg for {'str': 'inactive solar bot'}.
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "The solar bot's lights flicker on as it boots up successfully."
msgstr "太陽能機器人的燈光閃爍亮起，成功啟動。"

#. ~ Use action hostile_msg for {'str': 'inactive solar bot'}.
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "You misprogram the solar bot; it's hostile!"
msgstr "你錯誤編程了太陽能機器人；它變得敵對！"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'inactive solar bot'}
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid ""
"A salvaged riot-control bot awkwardly welded together with an experimental "
"laser turret. A layer of solar cells and blinking LED lights cover it's "
"hull. It's currently inactive and ready to be deployed."
msgstr "一個回收的防暴控制機器人被笨拙地焊接了一臺實驗性激光炮塔。其外殼覆蓋了一層太陽能電池和閃爍的LED燈。目前處於未激活狀態，已準備好部署。"

#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "broken security bot"
msgid_plural "broken security bots"
msgstr[0] "損壞的安保機器人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broken security bot'}
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid ""
"A broken security bot, now busted and helpless. It could be gutted for parts"
" or jury-rigged into a new type of bot."
msgstr "一個損壞的安保機器人，如今破損不堪、孤立無援。它可以被拆解獲取零件，或者臨時改裝成新型機器人。"

#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "broken killbot"
msgid_plural "broken killbots"
msgstr[0] "損壞的殺戮機器人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broken killbot'}
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid ""
"A broken killbot, now peaceful and still. It could be repaired or stripped "
"down to its security bot frame."
msgstr "一臺損壞的殺戮機器人，現在平靜而靜止。它可以被修復，或者拆解成其安保機器人框架。"

#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "inactive killbot"
msgid_plural "inactive killbots"
msgstr[0] "未激活的殺戮機器人"

#. ~ Use action friendly_msg for {'str': 'inactive killbot'}.
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "The killbot comes online and spins it chansaws in anticipation."
msgstr "殺戮機器人啟動上線，並興奮地旋轉著它的鏈鋸。"

#. ~ Use action hostile_msg for {'str': 'inactive killbot'}.
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "You misprogram the killbot! That ain't good."
msgstr "你錯誤編程了殺戮機器人！這可不太妙。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'inactive killbot'}
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid ""
"A salvaged security bot repurposed into a lumbering engine of destruction. "
"Extra layers of steel armor and a pair of chainsaws have been welded to the "
"chasis. It's currently inactive but ready to be deployed."
msgstr "一臺回收的安保機器人被改造成了一臺笨重的毀滅引擎。額外的鋼甲層和一對鏈鋸被焊接到底盤上。它目前處於未激活狀態，但已準備好部署。"

#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "broken chickenbot"
msgid_plural "broken chickenbots"
msgstr[0] "損壞的雞形機器人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broken chickenbot'}
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid ""
"A broken chicken walker, now headless and defeated. It could be gutted for "
"parts or jury-rigged into a new type of bot."
msgstr "一臺損壞的雞足步行機，現在已無頭且被擊敗。它可以被拆解獲取零件，或者臨時改裝成一種新型機器人。"

#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "broken murder machine"
msgid_plural "broken murder machines"
msgstr[0] "損壞的殺戮機器"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broken murder machine'}
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid ""
"A broken murder machine, now silent and mangled. It could be repaired or "
"stripped down to its original frame."
msgstr "一臺損壞的殺戮機器，現在沉默且扭曲。它可以被修復，或者拆解成其原始框架。"

#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "inactive murder machine"
msgid_plural "inactive murder machines"
msgstr[0] "未激活的殺戮機器"

#. ~ Use action friendly_msg for {'str': 'inactive murder machine'}.
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "The murder machine comes to life."
msgstr "殺戮機器甦醒過來。"

#. ~ Use action hostile_msg for {'str': 'inactive murder machine'}.
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "You misprogram the murder machine; it wants to murder you!"
msgstr "你錯誤編程了殺戮機器；它想殺了你！"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'inactive murder machine'}
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid ""
"A salvaged chicken walker, pieced back together into a shambling combat "
"robot that's more terrifying than effective. It is currently inactive and "
"ready to be deployed."
msgstr "一臺回收的雞足步行機，被重新拼湊成一個蹣跚的戰鬥機器人，與其說有效不如說更嚇人。它目前處於未激活狀態，已準備好部署。"

#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "broken tank drone"
msgid_plural "broken tank drones"
msgstr[0] "損壞的坦克無人機"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broken tank drone'}
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid ""
"A broken tank drone, lying in a heap of twisted metal. It could be gutted "
"for parts or jury-rigged into a new type of bot."
msgstr "一臺損壞的坦克無人機，躺在一堆扭曲的金屬中。它可以被拆解獲取零件，或者臨時改裝成一種新型機器人。"

#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "broken droidnaught"
msgid_plural "broken droidnaughts"
msgstr[0] "損壞的機器人無畏艦"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broken droidnaught'}
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid ""
"A broken droidnaught. It could be repaired or stripped down to its tank "
"frame."
msgstr "一臺損壞的機器人無畏艦。它可以被修復，或者拆解成其坦克框架。"

#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "inactive droidnaught"
msgid_plural "inactive droidnaughts"
msgstr[0] "未激活的機器人無畏艦"

#. ~ Use action friendly_msg for {'str': 'inactive droidnaught'}.
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "The droidnaught revs its engines as its systems comes online."
msgstr "機器人無畏艦在其系統上線時發動了引擎。"

#. ~ Use action hostile_msg for {'str': 'inactive droidnaught'}.
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "You have made a very serious mistake. The droidnaught is now hostile."
msgstr "你犯了一個非常嚴重的錯誤。機器人無畏艦現在變得敵對。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'inactive droidnaught'}
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid ""
"A gutted tank bot refurbished with vehicle parts and questionable wiring. "
"The cannon has been replaced with a rapid-fire pneumatic hammer. It is "
"currently inactive and ready to be deployed."
msgstr "一臺被掏空的坦克機器人，用車輛零件和可疑的線路進行了翻新。火炮已被替換為速射氣動錘。它目前處於未激活狀態，已準備好部署。"

#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "broken hazmatbot"
msgid_plural "broken hazmatbots"
msgstr[0] "損壞的防化機器人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broken hazmatbot'}
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid ""
"A broken HAZMAT bot, now polluted and shattered. It could be gutted for "
"parts or jury-rigged into a new type of bot."
msgstr "一臺損壞的HAZMAT機器人，現在已被汙染且破碎。它可以被拆解獲取零件，或者臨時改裝成一種新型機器人。"

#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "broken cleaner bot"
msgid_plural "broken cleaner bots"
msgstr[0] "損壞的清潔機器人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broken cleaner bot'}
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid ""
"A broken cleaner bot, now corroded and filthy. It could be repaired or "
"stripped down to its HAZMAT robot frame."
msgstr "一臺損壞的清潔機器人，現在已被腐蝕且骯髒。它可以被修復，或者拆解成其HAZMAT機器人框架。"

#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "inactive cleaner bot"
msgid_plural "inactive cleaner bots"
msgstr[0] "未激活的清潔機器人"

#. ~ Use action friendly_msg for {'str': 'inactive cleaner bot'}.
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid ""
"The cleanerbot charges up and begins bubbling over with noxious chemicals."
msgstr "清潔機器人充能完畢，並開始冒出有毒化學物質的氣泡。"

#. ~ Use action hostile_msg for {'str': 'inactive cleaner bot'}.
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid "You misprogram the cleaner bot!"
msgstr "你錯誤編程了清潔機器人！"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'inactive cleaner bot'}
#: .\jrr_items.json
msgid ""
"A salvaged HAZMAT robot refitted with second-hand circuits and plumbing "
"supplies. It cleans by spraying an area with caustic fluids from an internal"
" boiler. IT is currently inactive and waiting to be deployed."
msgstr ""
"一臺回收的HAZMAT機器人，用二手電路和管道供應品進行了改裝。它通過從內部鍋爐向區域噴灑腐蝕性液體來進行清潔。它目前處於未激活狀態，等待部署。"

#: .\jrr_monster_override.json
msgid "security bot"
msgid_plural "security bots"
msgstr[0] "安保機器人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'security bot'}
#: .\jrr_monster_override.json
msgid ""
"The Northrop Watchman X-1 is a production series of armored combat robots.  "
"Initially designed for military patrol and escort service, it rolls on a set"
" of hydraulic treads and is armed with twins SMGs."
msgstr "諾斯羅普守望者X-1是一款裝甲戰鬥機器人的生產系列。最初設計用於軍事巡邏和護送服務，它依靠一套液壓履帶移動，並配備雙聯SMG。"

#: .\jrr_monster_override.json
msgid "HAZMAT bot"
msgid_plural "HAZMAT bots"
msgstr[0] "危險品處理機器人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'HAZMAT bot'}
#: .\jrr_monster_override.json
msgid ""
"The Ford Sanitron, a utility robot designed for cleaning up waste material "
"in hazardous conditions."
msgstr "福特清潔機器人，一種專為在危險環境下清理廢棄物而設計的實用型機器人。"

#: .\jrr_monster_override.json
msgid "chicken walker"
msgid_plural "chicken walkers"
msgstr[0] "雞形步行機"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'chicken walker'}
#: .\jrr_monster_override.json
msgid ""
"The Northrop ATSV, a massive, heavily-armed and armored robot walking on a "
"pair of reverse-jointed legs.  Armed with a 40mm anti-vehicle grenade "
"launcher, 5.56 anti-personnel gun, and the ability to electrify itself "
"against attackers, it is an effective automated sentry, though production "
"was limited due to a legal dispute."
msgstr ""
"諾斯羅普ATSV，一種龐大、重武裝且重裝甲的機器人，以一對反關節腿行走。配備40毫米反車輛榴彈發射器、5.56毫米反人員槍械，並能對攻擊者釋放電擊，是一種高效的自動哨兵，但因法律糾紛生產受限。"

#: .\jrr_new_bots.json
msgid "pursuer drone"
msgid_plural "pursuer drones"
msgstr[0] "追擊無人機"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pursuer drone'}
#: .\jrr_new_bots.json
msgid ""
"A wheeled drone designed to pursue and exterminate enemy combatants. It's "
"capable of dispensing onboard manhacks to harry and weaken its prey."
msgstr "一種輪式無人機，旨在追擊並消滅敵方戰鬥人員。它能釋放機載的獵殺無人機來騷擾和削弱目標。"

#: .\jrr_new_bots.json
msgid "seeker drone"
msgid_plural "seeker drones"
msgstr[0] "搜尋無人機"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'seeker drone'}
#: .\jrr_new_bots.json
msgid ""
"An autonomous hoverdrone designed to seek and exterminate enemy combatants. "
"It's capable of delivering a single burst of 9mm rounds before closing in to"
" finish off its prey."
msgstr "一種自主懸浮無人機，旨在搜尋並消滅敵方戰鬥人員。它能發射一次9毫米子彈連射，然後靠近以終結目標。"

#: .\jrr_new_bots.json
msgid "hunter drone"
msgid_plural "hunter drones"
msgstr[0] "獵殺無人機"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'hunter drone'}
#: .\jrr_new_bots.json
msgid ""
"A dog-sized military drone designed to hunt down and exterminate enemy "
"combatants. With a pair of barbed mandibles, it can prevent its prey from "
"escaping."
msgstr "一種狗大小的軍用無人機，旨在追捕並消滅敵方戰鬥人員。憑藉一對帶刺的顎部，它能阻止目標逃脫。"

#: .\jrr_new_bots.json
msgid "chaser drone"
msgid_plural "chaser drones"
msgstr[0] "追逐無人機"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'chaser drone'}
#: .\jrr_new_bots.json
msgid ""
"A relentless hoverdrone designed to chase down and exterminate enemy robots."
" It's capable of firing nine .50bmg rounds before closing in to finish off "
"its prey."
msgstr "一種無情的懸浮無人機，旨在追擊並消滅敵方機器人。它能發射九發.50 BMG子彈，然後靠近以終結目標。"

#: .\jrr_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Robotics Intern"
msgstr "機器人實習生"

#: .\jrr_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Robotics Intern"
msgstr "機器人實習生"

#. ~ Profession (male Robotics Intern) description
#: .\jrr_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"After months of online courses, you finally got your first internship in the"
" field of robotics. Unfortunately, the Cataclysm has put a premature end to "
"your career."
msgstr "經過數月的在線課程，你終於在機器人領域獲得了第一份實習工作。不幸的是，大災變過早地終結了你的職業生涯。"

#. ~ Profession (female Robotics Intern) description
#: .\jrr_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"After months of online courses, you finally got your first internship in the"
" field of robotics. Unfortunately, the Cataclysm has put a premature end to "
"your career."
msgstr "經過數月的在線課程，你終於在機器人領域獲得了第一份實習工作。不幸的是，大災變過早地終結了你的職業生涯。"

#: .\jrr_rigged_bots.json
msgid "distractron"
msgid_plural "distractrons"
msgstr[0] "干擾機器人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'distractron'}
#: .\jrr_rigged_bots.json
msgid ""
"A manhack hastily rewired into a distraction device. Its main blades have "
"been removed, making it harmless, but also more difficult to hit. Mp3's of "
"pre-Cataclysmic folk music have been added as a further distraction."
msgstr ""
"一臺被匆忙改造成干擾裝置的獵殺無人機。其主要葉片已被移除，使其無害，但也更難被擊中。作為進一步的干擾手段，還添加了大災變前的民謠音樂MP3。"

#: .\jrr_rigged_bots.json
msgid "venomhack"
msgid_plural "venomhacks"
msgstr[0] "毒刺無人機"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'venomhack'}
#: .\jrr_rigged_bots.json
msgid ""
"A salvaged manhack tinkered into a venomous drone. The stingers of giant "
"insects have been added in place of blades."
msgstr "一臺經過改造的獵殺無人機，被改裝成帶毒無人機。巨型昆蟲的毒刺被用來替代葉片。"

#: .\jrr_rigged_bots.json
msgid "smokehack"
msgid_plural "smokehacks"
msgstr[0] "煙霧無人機"

#: .\jrr_rigged_bots.json
msgid "orb bot"
msgid_plural "orb bots"
msgstr[0] "球型機器人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'orb bot'}
#: .\jrr_rigged_bots.json
msgid ""
"A salvaged eyebot patched up with low-grade electronics and equipped with a "
"powerful floodlight. It wobbles unsteadily in the air."
msgstr "一臺用低端電子元件修復的回收眼球機器人，並配備了一盞強力泛光燈。它在空中搖晃不定。"

#: .\jrr_rigged_bots.json
msgid "skaterbot"
msgid_plural "skaterbots"
msgstr[0] "滑行機器人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'skaterbot'}
#: .\jrr_rigged_bots.json
msgid ""
"A salvaged skitterbot with wheels kludged to the ends of its insectoid legs."
" It sparks dangerously as it moves across the ground and omits a faint smell"
" of ozone."
msgstr "一臺回收的疾行機器人，其昆蟲般的腿部末端被笨拙地加裝了輪子。它在地面移動時會危險地冒出火花，並散發出微弱的臭氧味。"

#: .\jrr_rigged_bots.json
msgid "shock bot"
msgid_plural "shock bots"
msgstr[0] "電擊機器人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'shock bot'}
#: .\jrr_rigged_bots.json
msgid ""
"A salvaged police bot mended with old circuit boards and car batteries. It's"
" been covered with electrified barbed wire and given a makeshift shock gun. "
"With its safety protocols wiped, the shockbot no longer respects police "
"authority or cares much for the safety of its allies."
msgstr ""
"一臺用舊電路板和汽車電池修復的回收警察機器人。它被覆蓋著帶電的鐵絲網，並配備了一把臨時電擊槍。由於安全協議被清除，電擊機器人不再尊重警察權威，也不太關心盟友的安全。"

#: .\jrr_rigged_bots.json
msgid "solar bot"
msgid_plural "solar bots"
msgstr[0] "太陽能機器人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'solar bot'}
#: .\jrr_rigged_bots.json
msgid ""
"A salvaged riot-control bot awkwardly welded together with an experimental "
"laser turret. A layer of solar cells and blinking LED lights cover it's "
"hull."
msgstr "一臺回收的防暴控制機器人，與一門實驗性激光炮塔笨拙地焊接在一起。其外殼覆蓋著一層太陽能電池和閃爍的LED燈。"

#: .\jrr_rigged_bots.json
msgid "killbot"
msgid_plural "killbots"
msgstr[0] "殺戮機器人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'killbot'}
#: .\jrr_rigged_bots.json
msgid ""
"A salvaged security bot repurposed into a lumbering engine of destruction. "
"Extra layers of mismatched armor plates and a pair of chainsaws have been "
"welded to the chassis."
msgstr "一臺回收的安全機器人，被改造成一臺笨重的毀滅引擎。額外的錯配裝甲板和一對鏈鋸被焊接到底盤上。"

#: .\jrr_rigged_bots.json
msgid "unholy murder machine"
msgid_plural "unholy murder machines"
msgstr[0] "邪惡殺戮機器"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'unholy murder machine'}
#: .\jrr_rigged_bots.json
msgid ""
"A salvaged chickenbot, pieced back together into a shambling combat robot "
"that's more terrifying than effective. The flamethrower has been converted "
"into a smoke generator, and the grenade launcher removed to make room for "
"extra belts of 5.56 ammo. For intimidation, rusty spikes and grisly junk "
"adorn the murder machine's hull while loudspeakers play earsplitting "
"shrieks."
msgstr ""
"一臺回收的雞型機器人，被拼湊成一個蹣跚的戰鬥機器人，其恐怖程度遠超實用性。火焰噴射器被改造成煙霧發生器，榴彈發射器被移除，為額外的5.56毫米彈藥帶騰出空間。為了恐嚇，生鏽的尖刺和可怕的垃圾裝飾著這臺殺戮機器的外殼，同時揚聲器播放著刺耳的尖叫聲。"

#: .\jrr_rigged_bots.json
msgid "droidnaught"
msgid_plural "droidnaughts"
msgstr[0] "無畏機器人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'droidnaught'}
#: .\jrr_rigged_bots.json
msgid ""
"A gutted tank bot refurbished with vehicle parts and questionable wiring. "
"The cannon has been replaced with a rapid-fire pneumatic hammer."
msgstr "一臺被掏空的坦克機器人，用車輛零件和可疑線路翻新而成。火炮已被替換為速射氣動錘。"

#: .\jrr_rigged_bots.json
msgid "cleaner bot"
msgid_plural "cleaner bots"
msgstr[0] "清潔機器人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cleaner bot'}
#: .\jrr_rigged_bots.json
msgid ""
"A salvaged HAZMAT robot refitted with second-hand circuits and plumbing "
"supplies. It cleans by spraying caustic fluids from an internal boiler. "
"Although not meant for combat, it can burn enemies effectively."
msgstr "一臺回收的HAZMAT機器人，改裝了二手電路和管道配件。它通過內部鍋爐噴灑腐蝕性液體進行清潔。雖非為戰鬥設計，但能有效灼傷敵人。"

#: .\jrr_speech.json
msgid "smooth polka beats."
msgstr "流暢的波爾卡節拍。"

#: .\jrr_speech.json
msgid "Amazon drumming."
msgstr "亞馬遜鼓點。"

#: .\jrr_speech.json
msgid "Mongolian throat singing."
msgstr "蒙古呼麥。"

#: .\jrr_speech.json
msgid "the relaxing tones of the didgeridoo."
msgstr "迪吉里杜管的舒緩音調。"

#: .\jrr_speech.json
msgid "traditional Punjabi wedding music."
msgstr "傳統的旁遮普婚禮音樂。"

#: .\jrr_speech.json
msgid "a claw hammer banjo."
msgstr "一把爪錘班卓琴。"

#: .\jrr_speech.json
msgid "a strumming ukulele."
msgstr "彈奏的尤克里裡。"

#: .\jrr_speech.json
msgid "wild Roma fiddling."
msgstr "狂野的羅姆小提琴演奏。"

#: .\jrr_speech.json
msgid "rustic sea shanties."
msgstr "質樸的海上船歌。"

#: .\jrr_speech.json
msgid "a nose harp."
msgstr "鼻豎琴。"

#: .\jrr_speech.json
msgid "echoing Calypso music."
msgstr "迴盪的卡利普索音樂。"

#: .\jrr_speech.json
msgid "the sound of Neuvo Tango."
msgstr "新探戈的聲音。"

#: .\jrr_speech.json
msgid "a buzzing hurdy gurdy."
msgstr "嗡嗡作響的手搖風琴。"

#: .\jrr_speech.json
msgid "folk music."
msgstr "民間音樂。"

#: .\jrr_vehicle.json
msgid "Clever Cab"
msgstr "靈巧出租車"

#: .\jrr_vehicle.json
msgid "Bionic Bus"
msgstr "仿生巴士"

#: .\jrr_vehicle.json
msgid "SWAT Pacifier"
msgstr "特警安撫者"

#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Jury-Rigged Robots"
msgstr "臨時拼裝機器人"

#. ~ Description for Jury-Rigged Robots
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"Adds various options for salvaging, jury rigging, and reprogramming broken "
"robots."
msgstr "為打撈、臨時拼裝和重編程損壞的機器人添加了多種選項。"
